      "evidence": "require-tdd-state.sh counts every approved exception for the cycle and requires each ID to have a granted audit event. run-second-opinion.sh writes approved review-completion entries but appends audit event obligation_completed, not granted. After any review completion exists, typed test-edit exceptions in the same cycle can be disabled by the missing-grant check.",
